'''Sektor 242 NewsLine''' was a smaller news agency during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], but it attained a high standard concerning accuracy and objectivity. This network also had one of the most popular [[holostrip]]s in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]], "[[The Times and Trepidations of Majnar Roak]]."

Sektor 242 Newsline filed a report from [[Queo City]] on [[Stend VI]] on the situation surrounding the seeming disappearance of the [[Khuiumin Survivors]].<ref name="J10">{{JournalCite|10|Galaxywide NewsNets}}</ref>

